  "id": "RAW_7cb15359",
  "title": "奖励模型变天！0.005%参数量推理速度翻倍，性能还更强",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652667206&idx=3&sn=de89f9cb992420e7f186fad26fe16790",
  "date": "2026-01-23 05:13:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb3GPr5ef2nr16IkZtBTTaib17NWicX9phO5xOfa90UROSTQsSJJ1Zv532q9ybDynpZOYvLmO2IyPibDQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"505182201\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ecabb2bd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3GPr5ef2nr16IkZtBTTaib17NWicX9phO5xOfa90UROSTQsSJJ1Zv532q9ybDynpZOYvLmO2IyPibDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：LRST</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">最新奖励模型</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">SWIFT直接利用模型生成过程中的隐藏状态，参数规模极小，仅占传统模型的不到0.005%。SWIFT在多个基准测试中表现优异，推理速度提升1.7×–6.7×，且在对齐评估中稳定可靠，展现出高效、通用的奖励建模新范式。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在大语言模型的推理增强与对齐过程中，Best-of-N（优中选优）是一种常用的测试时增强策略：模型针对同一输入生成多条候选答案，再由奖励模型进行评分筛选。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，现有主流奖励模型往往本身规模庞大、推理开销高，并严重依赖大规模标注数据，逐渐成为在真实系统中部署的核心瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为此，上海交通大学、新加坡国立大学、同济大学、伊利诺伊大学芝加哥分校的研究团队提出了</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT（Simple Weighted Intrinsic Feedback Technique）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，一种全新的轻量级奖励模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32456935630099726\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2206\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2206\" data-height=\"716\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"182\" data-imgfileid=\"505181453\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5724c63a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKfzsOic3NHRWcqlF1FzzYqz9lKLk0JdtoAAvqatroLOWtk6shnTicyK7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.12225\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.12225</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">项目主页：<a href=\"https://aster2024.github.io/swift-website/\" target=\"_blank\">https://aster2024.github.io/swift-website/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">代码地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/aster2024/SWIFT\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/aster2024/SWIFT</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">模型权重：<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Aster2024/swift-ministral-8b-deepscaler\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/Aster2024/swift-ministral-8b-deepscaler</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT 不再「读文本」，而是直接利用大语言模型生成过程中产生的隐藏状态，从中挖掘内在奖励信号，其参数规模仅为传统奖励模型的「</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不到 0.005%」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，却在MATH、GSM8K、HellaSwag 等多个基准上取得更优的Best-of-N效果，并在端到端推理中带来</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.7×–6.7×</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的整体加速。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，该方法在</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有用性 / 安全性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">等对齐评估任务中同样表现稳定，展示出作为通用奖励模型的潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">奖励模型</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">推理增强的「隐形天花板」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Best-of-N的基本思想并不复杂：对于同一个问题生成N条候选回答，再挑选其中最优的一条。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，在真实系统中，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">真正昂贵的不仅是「多生成」，还有「如何评估」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当前主流做法通常采用文本级奖励模型，对每条候选答案进行完整编码和评分，这带来了多方面的挑战：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型体量大、推理开销高</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：奖励模型往往拥有数十亿参数，几乎相当于再运行一次大模型；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据需求高</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：训练高度依赖人工偏好数据或复杂的合成标注流程；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">系统扩展受限</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：当 N 增大时，奖励模型的评估成本迅速吞噬 Best-of-N 带来的收益。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因此，一个关键问题逐渐凸显：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">能否用一种更轻、更快、更易部署的方式，完成候选答案的高质量筛选？</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">隐藏状态中蕴含着模型「对自己答案的判断」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT 的出发点来自一个重要观察：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">当大语言模型生成回答时，其内部各层的隐藏状态本身就携带了关于推理正确性、稳定性与置信度的丰富信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">换句话说，模型在「思考」的过程中，已经在内部形成了对当前推理路径质量的判断信号。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与其额外训练一个庞大的文本模型去「读输出结果」，不如</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">直接从模型自身的隐藏状态中提取这些内在信号</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，构建一个专门用于打分的轻量级奖励模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一思路使得奖励建模不再依赖复杂的文本表示，而是转向对模型内部表示的高效利用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">词元级线性打分+门控加权汇总</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT的整体结构非常简洁，但针对奖励建模的需求进行了精心设计，具体而言：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于生成序列中的每一个</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">词元</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，收集大语言模型在该词元处的隐藏状态（来自所有层，或选定的部分层）；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过一个线性映射，同时预测「该词元的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">奖励分数」和「</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">该词元的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">重要性门控权重」</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">使用门控权重对词元奖励进行加权平均，得到整条生成路径的最终奖励分数。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中，门控机制使模型能够自动关注对最终正确性更关键的词元（如关键推理步骤、数值计算、结论标记等），从而对整条推理轨迹进行更精细的评估。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">整个奖励模型的参数规模仅与「层数 × 隐藏维度」成正比，相比传统文本奖励模型实现了数量级的压缩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4583333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1996\" data-height=\"914\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"258\" data-imgfileid=\"505181454\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f458dad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKdY3kJxrWnEYqdetng9SsbHoMXurAmZ00XqiajCMHVwsYsniaxEPge23g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">如此轻量</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">参数规模与训练成本的数量级差距</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与动辄数十亿参数的传统奖励模型相比，SWIFT的参数规模仅为</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">10⁵量级</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，在不同底座模型上的具体数值均远低于现有主流方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">论文在参数量与训练数据规模的对比中显示：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT不仅模型规模极小，训练所需的数据量也显著更低，却依然能够取得具有竞争力甚至更优的性能表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一特性使得SWIFT在资源受限环境或大规模部署场景中具备明显优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqezpv51936\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8264705882352941\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"680\" style=\"width: 79%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"680\" data-height=\"562\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"464\" data-imgfileid=\"505181452\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=766ab56f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKIw4ppYaoSG9mb2DMHW72FNLqVUD1nMBRcaSYSu9iaNFyTTzXJSzqDhQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">在多个基准上全面超越主流奖励模型</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在数学推理与符号推理等核心基准上，研究团队系统评估了SWIFT在Best-of-N设置下的表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在MATH、GSM8K、AQuA-RAT、Imbue Code Comprehension、HellaSwag、CoinFlip数据集上，SWIFT在不同底座模型与不同N值配置下，整体准确率均优于多种主流开源奖励模型，且表现更加稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更重要的是，这些性能提升并非以高昂计算代价为前提。论文进一步报告了端到端推理流程中的实际耗时：在相同的生成设置下，用SWIFT替换传统奖励模型，可带来1</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">.7×–6.7×</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的整体加速。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39444444444444443\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2208\" data-height=\"870\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"222\" data-imgfileid=\"505181456\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c2053a86&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKHvI9DyhaibEdr9OjBGcfdhxvfNRW8U4lRwU9PnOF5JJng9USTxEheBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">效率优势</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">时间与计算量均达到「数量级提升」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在真实系统中，推理效率往往比离线指标更具决定性意义。论文通过对比每条样本的平均耗时与计算量，清晰展示了SWIFT在效率上的优势：平均推理时间显著降低；所需计算量（FLOPs）减少到原有方法的极小一部分；在不同数据集和底座模型组合下均保持一致趋势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果表明，SWIFT在效率层面实现了真正意义上的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数量级优势</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，为大规模 Best-of-N推理提供了可行路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38055555555555554\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2450\" data-height=\"932\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"214\" data-imgfileid=\"505181455\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f0f7d94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKsx1KjTtmQ95uytvIuqhRcyZCuOlia7DTGpc7xDDLpKgHQCiccXdP7jpg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">从推理到对齐</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">在有用性/安全性评估中表现</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">稳定</span></strong></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT并不局限于推理准确率的提升。研究团队进一步在对齐相关评估任务中验证了其通用性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在PKU-SafeRLHF数据集上，采用Best-of-N设置，并使用强模型作为评判标准，对生成结果的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有用性与安全性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">进行评估。结果显示，SWIFT在这两个维度上均优于多种大规模文本奖励模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一结果表明，隐藏状态中蕴含的信息不仅能够反映推理正确性，也能刻画更广义的响应质量，为奖励模型在对齐评估中的应用提供了新的思路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.14444444444444443\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2194\" data-height=\"316\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"81\" data-imgfileid=\"505181457\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67722830&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKDxOVk89S3KXacMRlV43ickuPoBg4lIwrKK6picJNgicdPeqnbtKI5Qrbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">工程化优势</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">更轻、更快、与传统奖励模型协同</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT 还展示了多种面向工程落地的扩展方式，使其不仅具备理论上的简洁性，也具备现实系统中的高度可用性：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">部分层训练</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：消融实验进一步表明，相比模型前层，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">靠近输出的后层隐藏状态包含更强的推理正确性信号</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。仅使用少数后层训练 SWIFT，便可在显著减少参数规模与计算开销的同时，保持与使用全部层时接近的性能。这一结果说明，SWIFT 主要依赖模型在形成最终判断阶段的内部表示，而非早期的表层语言特征。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">仅基于输出分布（logits）的训练方式</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：在无法访问隐藏状态的场景下，SWIFT 仍可仅依赖模型的输出分布进行训练。实验结果表明，即使在这种受限设定下，SWIFT 依然能够提取到具有判别力的质量信号。这一特性使其在一定程度上具备与部分闭源大模型兼容的可行性，显著拓宽了实际应用边界。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与传统奖励模型组合</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：得益于极小的参数规模（不足传统奖励模型的 0.005%），将 SWIFT 与现有奖励模型进行组合几乎不会引入额外的系统开销。论文探索了基于排序选择与加权融合的简单策略，实验表明，在多个基准上，这种组合方式能够进一步提升推理准确率。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">综合来看，这些工程化特性使 SWIFT 不仅可以作为传统奖励模型的高效替代方案，也能够作为现有奖励模型体系中的轻量级补充模块，在几乎不增加部署成本的前提下提升整体系统性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">总结</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">奖励建模的新范式</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SWIFT 提供了一条不同于「更大模型、更重计算」的奖励建模路径：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">直接利用大模型内部隐藏状态中的内在信号；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以极低的参数与数据成本，实现高效、稳定的奖励评估；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时兼顾推理增强与对齐评估，具备良好的工程落地潜力。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这项工作表明，在大模型推理与对齐领域，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">性能提升并不一定依赖于更复杂的外部模型，而可能来自对模型自身内部机制的更深入理解与利用</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.12225\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.12225</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "上海交大等机构提出 SWIFT 轻量级奖励模型，通过挖掘大模型内部隐藏状态实现极低参数量的快速推理与高效对齐。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "上海交大等机构提出 SWIFT 轻量级奖励模型，通过挖掘大模型内部隐藏状态实现极低参数量的快速推理与高效对齐。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了一种名为 SWIFT 的新型轻量级奖励模型，旨在解决传统奖励模型参数规模大、推理成本高及依赖大规模标注数据的问题。SWIFT 的核心创新在于不再对生成的文本进行二次编码，而是直接提取大语言模型在生成过程中产生的隐藏状态作为奖励信号。该模型采用词元级线性打分与门控加权机制，参数量仅为传统模型的 0.005%，但在 MATH、GSM8K 等基准测试中表现优于主流模型，且能实现 1.7x 至 6.7x 的端到端推理加速。此外，SWIFT 在安全性与有用性评估中也展现出极强的通用性与工程化潜力。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "SWIFT 直接利用模型内部隐藏状态而非文本表示进行奖励建模。",
      "explanation": "通过挖掘模型生成过程中的内在信号，避免了对候选答案的重复编码，极大地降低了计算开销和参数规模。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用词元级线性打分结合门控机制实现精细化评估。",
      "explanation": "模型为每个词元预测奖励分数和重要性权重，使系统能自动聚焦于关键推理步骤或数值计算，提升评分准确性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在极低资源消耗下实现了超越大规模奖励模型的性能。",
      "explanation": "仅需 10^5 级参数量，在多个数学和逻辑推理基准测试中，其 Best-of-N 筛选效果优于数十亿参数的传统模型。"
    },
    {
      "point": "具备极强的工程落地灵活性与协同能力。",
      "explanation": "支持仅基于后层隐藏状态或输出分布训练，且能与现有奖励模型无缝组合，在不增加部署成本的前提下提升系统表现。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "SWIFT 不再「读文本」，而是直接利用大语言模型生成过程中产生的隐藏状态，从中挖掘内在奖励信号。",
    "其参数规模仅为传统奖励模型的「不到 0.005%」，却在多个基准上取得更优的 Best-of-N 效果。",
    "在相同的生成设置下，用 SWIFT 替换传统奖励模型，可带来 1.7×--6.7× 的整体加速。",
    "性能提升并不一定依赖于更复杂的外部模型，而可能来自对模型自身内部机制的更深入理解与利用。"
  ],
